How are you?;Genki desu ka
What time is it?;Nanji desu ka
What is your name?;Onamae wa nan desu ka
Can you hear me?;Koe ga kikoemasu ka
Is it far?;Tōi desu ka
Are you ready;Junbi wa ii desu ka
What’s new?;Nanika atarashii desu ka
Did you sleep well?;Yoku nemuremashita ka
Where were you?;Doko ni imashita ka
What are you doing?;Nani o shite imasu ka
Are you hungry?;Onaka ga sukimashita ka
How was your day?;Kyō wa dō deshita ka
What are you planning to do?;Nani o suru keikaku desu ka
How are you feeling?;Kibun wa dō desu ka
Do you have any plans?;Yotei wa arimasu ka
How is your family?;Kazoku wa genki desu ka
Do you like it here?;Koko wa suki desu ka
When are you free?;Itsu ga hima desu ka
What happened?;Dō shita n desu ka
